.SH NAME
cik_asic_reset \- soft reset GPU
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" cik_asic_reset
.BI "(struct radeon_device *rdev "  ","
.BI "bool hard "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "rdev" 12
radeon_device pointer
.IP "hard" 12
force hard reset
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Look up which blocks are hung and attempt
to reset them.
Returns 0 for success.
